Clone the repository:
                     git clone https://github.com/BhupendraTiwari-11/currency-converter.git cd currency-converter
Install dependencies: Install the required Pillow library using pip:
                      pip install Pillow

Run the application:
                    python currency_converter.py
Note: If python doesn't work, try python3 depending on your system configuration:
                     python3 currency_converter.py
